From 6845f14867158e74211888517974d45eb4943e47 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Balamurugan Mahalingam <bmahalin@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 21 May 2025 21:20:37 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 03/11] QSDK:DP:wifi Add support for handling vendor command to
 config ppe vp type

The vendor command interface allows the userspace application to
configure and query the PPE VP type for a netdevice.
The PPE VP type decides the datapath route the netdevice will utilize.

Patch-dependency:
        325-QSDK-DP-wifi-Add-support-for-PPE-DS-Direct-switch-fe.patch
Patch-work: None

Signed-off-by: Balamurugan Mahalingam <bmahalin@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Bhagavathi Perumal S <bperumal@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Neha Bisht <nbisht@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/Makefile |   1 +
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/vendor.c | 192 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/vendor.h |  75 +++++++++
 3 files changed, 268 insertions(+)
